      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is being listed honestly at a significantly reduced price to reflect its true current condition \u2014 it is in poor shape and should be approached as a project car or parts vehicle. The exterior shows substantial wear: paint is faded, scratched, and has areas of rust or peeling clear coat. Body panels may have dents or damage beyond minor cosmetic issues. Mechanically, the car has known issues that will require attention \u2014 expect repairs to be needed before this vehicle is reliably drivable. The interior shows heavy wear with torn or damaged upholstery, and some features may not function properly. This is a straightforward listing for a buyer who understands what they're taking on: a car in poor condition priced accordingly. No surprises \u2014 what you see is what you get, and we encourage a thorough inspection before purchase.",
