    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "\ud83d\udd27 Affordable Project Car with Potential! \u2014 Looking for a budget-friendly vehicle to work on or use for parts? This car is priced to reflect its current condition honestly \u2014 it has seen better days and will require meaningful mechanical and cosmetic attention before it's road-ready. That said, it's a great opportunity for a skilled DIYer or hobbyist who enjoys a hands-on challenge. The bones are there \u2014 come take a look and see what you can make of it! Sold as-is, priced accordingly.",
      "price": 5000.0,
