      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in good condition and represents a dependable, well-maintained used car that is ready for its next owner. The exterior shows typical signs of normal use \u2014 you'll notice some light surface scratches and minor scuffs consistent with everyday driving, but there are no significant dents, deep gouges, or rust issues. The paint retains a reasonable shine and presents well from a normal viewing distance. The interior is clean and functional, with some expected wear on high-contact areas such as the driver's seat, steering wheel, and door panels, but nothing that detracts from comfortable daily use. Mechanically, the car runs reliably and has been kept up with routine maintenance; all major systems are in good working order. This is an honest, solid used car \u2014 not a showroom-fresh example, but a genuinely dependable vehicle at a fair price.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed at $18,500, a price that honestly reflects its fair condition. The exterior shows visible signs of use \u2014 you can expect several scratches, a minor dent or two, and some areas where the paint has dulled or faded over time. It's not a showroom car, but it presents reasonably well from a normal viewing distance. The interior has seen regular use: the upholstery shows wear on the seat bolsters and high-contact areas, and there may be minor scuffs on trim panels, though nothing is torn or broken. Mechanically, the car runs and drives as expected for its age and mileage \u2014 routine maintenance has been performed, but as with any used vehicle in this condition range, a buyer should anticipate that some upcoming service items or minor repairs may be needed. This is a solid, honest, everyday driver that will serve a practical buyer well, priced fairly to reflect exactly what it is.",
      "price": 18500.0,
